review.reviewText:
Top notch accommodation with just a few notes:
- View lounge was closed for renovations;
- Knife-edge hot water valve in the bathroom sink meant scalding or frigid with no middle ground;
- As in many hotels, it takes 3 days to get the 3 bars of soap needed for 2 people using shower and sink;
- The room safe failed shut on the 3rd day.  They need to be redesigned as internet nodes so that batteries can be replaced in a timely manner or as AC appliances.
